<Author>nascot
<Content>Nice but noisy I spent 2 nights in the hotel during the week staying in a single room. The room was clean and tidy and all the furniture was in good condition. The bathroom was clean and in fully working order. A little pack next to the sink contained toothpaste, toothbrush, soap, shower gel, shampoo and conditioner. The breakfast area was small but clean and served the usual standard euro selection of cereal, cheese and cold meat. The only downside to the hotel was how little soundproofing my room had. I could hear people going up and down stairs and shutting doors etc although some of this has to do with fellow guests lack of consideration.The hotel location is futher from the train station (Sants) then the website suggests. They say 500m but I'd say it's closer to 1000m! It's a 15/20 min walk to the top of La Rambla.All in all it was a pleasent stay and I would recommend it for a 1 or 2 night stay. 
